    <item>
      <title>由于出口商受日元下跌影响，日本股市自 10 月份以来跌幅最大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/nikkei-tumbles-most-in-a-year-as-yen-rise-weighs-on-exporters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本股市自 10 月 4 日以来跌幅最大，两个基准指数均下跌超过 2%，原因是日本央行将加息的猜测不断升温，推高了日元并损害了出口商。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/nikkei-tumbles-most-in-a-year-as-yen-rise-weighs-on-exporters</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 02:56:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>监管机构称银行家向韩国退休人员歪曲了与中国相关的高风险票据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/watchdog-says-bankers-misrepresented-risky-china-linked-notes-to-korean-retirees</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国金融监管机构表示，调查发现该国一些最大的经纪商向散户投资者歪曲了与中国相关的高风险结构性产品，并正在考虑采取包括处罚和禁止销售在内的补救措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/watchdog-says-bankers-misrepresented-risky-china-linked-notes-to-korean-retirees</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 01:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
