      <title>随着美国消费者物价指数 (CPI) 的关注，欧洲期货下跌，日元上涨：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-10/asian-stocks-to-fall-as-us-cpi-shifts-into-focus-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲股指期货下跌，交易员将注意力转向周二公布的美国通胀数据，以寻找未来美联储降息时机的线索。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-10/asian-stocks-to-fall-as-us-cpi-shifts-into-focus-markets-wrap</guid>
