    <item>
      <title>快时尚利润率和沙特阿美资本支出将在下周欧洲、中东和非洲地区盈利中占据主导地位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/fast-fashion-margins-aramco-s-capex-to-dominate-in-emea-earnings-next-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着欧洲财报季接近尾声，时尚零售商 Zalando SE 和 Inditex SA 本周接手了这一重任。随着低成本竞争对手的紧随其后，他们正在努力提高利润并将库存保持在可管理的水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/fast-fashion-margins-aramco-s-capex-to-dominate-in-emea-earnings-next-week</guid>
